                    <div class="content-box">
                        <p class="font-bold text-blue-700">English : </p>
                        <p class="mb-2">Crocodiles are usually found in Africa  ,  America  ,  Asia  ,  and Australia. They first appeared 240 million years ago. There are 23 different species  ,  with saltwater crocodiles being the biggest. They can grow to be 6 metres and weigh 1  ,  000 kilograms.</p>
